de.hsrm.diogenes.map
Class Map

java.lang.Object
  de.hsrm.diogenes.map.Map

public class Map
extends java.lang.Object

Class gets the map data from the robot, writes it into a file, then parses the file into the program and saves it as a MapFile object.

Author:
Dirk Stanke
